title: Utility Excavation Moratorium Streets
description: Street segments and intersections that have been paved within the last 5 years

columns.name: CNN
columns.description: CNN of street segment or intersection

columns.name: Limits
columns.description: A description of location combining from_st, to_st, cardinal and addrange

columns.name: JobOrderNum
columns.description: Job Order Number - a code for funding - under which street was paved

columns.name: ExpirationDate
columns.description: End of utility excavtion moratorium for location

columns.name: ModifiedDate
columns.description: date record was added or modified

columns.name: Neighborhoods
columns.description: This column was automatically created in order to record in what polygon from the dataset 'Neighborhoods' (jwn9-ihcz) the point in column 'point' is located.  This enables the creation of region maps (choropleths) in the visualization canvas and data lens.
